# Research Pipeline — Example
# This is an example file. Copy to memory/semantic/research-pipeline.md and fill in your details.
# CONSTITUTION §8: The live file is gitignored. Only this .example is committed.
# Updated by research-coach.md, 04_research-cycle.md, and 11_session-closer.md.

---

## Active Research Threads

> One entry per research thread. A thread = a distinct research direction or sub-problem.
> Update lifecycle stage as the thread progresses.

### Thread 1: [Short Title]
hypothesis: ""
# The key claim this thread is testing or the artefact it is building

methodology: ""
# Empirical / Design Science / Survey / Case Study / Mixed

lifecycle_stage: "ideation"
# Options: ideation | data-collection | analysis | writing | under-review | published | parked

publication_target: ""
# Planned publication venue (journal or conference) for this thread's output

cross_links:
  publication_log: null
  # Entry ID in memory/semantic/publication-log.md once a paper is submitted

last_updated: "YYYY-MM-DD"
notes: ""

---

