## Parked Threads

> Ideas that are paused — not abandoned, but not actively being developed.

| Thread | Reason Parked | Parked Date | Reopen Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| [short title] | [reason] | YYYY-MM-DD | [condition that would make it worth resuming] |

